00:00:57,653 --> 00:01:03,037
considered with both the dramatic and the domestic and it's an ensemble cast story so it's very much

15
00:01:03,077 --> 00:01:08,901
a soap opera in those terms and the mutant bit is fairly clear from this cast picture which you can

16
00:01:08,941 --> 00:01:14,705
see here. It's a 2D adventure game mostly focused on exploration, conversations,

