So in Matasiona you explore a community as a 15 year old girl called Kai. Kai sets out

19
00:01:27,490 --> 00:01:32,294
at the beginning of the game to head to the community in order to care for her dying grandfather.

20
00:01:32,894 --> 00:01:36,798
He thinks that he's bringing her there to train as a replacement spiritual leader for

21
00:01:36,918 --> 00:01:39,160
his strange and isolated town of Park Mutants.

22
00:01:39,631 --> 00:01:43,613
