23
00:01:43,973 --> 00:01:46,315
And the answers are in the community itself.

24
00:01:47,255 --> 00:01:51,738
So Mitassione is this world of weird and wonderful flora and fauna and a community

25
00:01:51,758 --> 00:01:54,459
cast of characters of many different shapes, sizes and colours.

26
00:01:55,099 --> 00:01:59,041
There are really beautiful landscapes to explore and this magical musical gardening

27
